Trigger 

 

TRG-01: The user clicks on the button “add hotel information” 

    

Post-Condition 

 

POS-01: A hotel information has been created 

    

Normal Flow  

      

1 

View a list hotel 

1. Users click on the tab “Add hotel information” in the right corner button 

2. The system redirects the user to the additional hotel information screen, which will display as follows: 

      One. Enter hotel information including: name, phone, address, description and email. 

      b. Hotel create button and close button 

3. After entering all information, the user clicks on the button “add hotel information” 

4. The system moves to the View hotel list screen
